#### Metagenomics: A New Perspective

The ability to sequence vast numbers of [genomes](/Genome) has led to a [metagenomic](/Metagenomic) approach to understanding the [tree of life](/Tree_of_life_(biology)). This reveals that bacteria are the most numerous life forms and that all life shares a common origin. [124](/Life#cite_note-124) [137](/Life#cite_note-137)

